snippet: An analysis based on matching names of White House visitors with names of Democratic donors indicates that those who gave more were more likely to visit or have meetings at the White House.
lead_paragraph: An analysis based on matching names of White House visitors with names of Democratic donors indicates that those who gave more were more likely to visit or have meetings at the White House.
